column1: do; the placeholder verb; something involving SBJ (subject) and OBJ (direct object) and IND (indirect object),
happen; SBJ (event) is a clause, wrapped in this clause,
true; yes; SBJ (truth) is a noun phrase that has an affirmative truth value (AMOUNT: truthiness; truth); antonym of "false",
false; no; SBJ (falsehood) is a noun phrase that has a negative truth value (AMOUNT: falseness); antonym of "true",
be; copula; SBJ is the same thing as OBJ (thing),
exist; be; SBJ (reality) is in some reality,
begin; start; become; SBJ transitions from falsehood to truth; antonym of "end",
continue; happen progressively; SBJ is occurring for some time,
end; stop; unbecome; cease; SBJ transitions from truth to falsehood
change; transition; translate; from; to; SBJ changes its state from IND (origin; initial; ablative) to OBJ (destination; final; lative),
undo; the action contrary to SBJ happens,
repeat; again; SBJ happens after having happened already,
cause; force; make; SBJ causes OBJ to happen,
necessary; need; must; SBJ (requisite; requirement) must be true in order for OBJ to be true,
imply; if; SBJ will happen if OBJ (condition) happens,
should; good; SBJ (decision) should happen to maximise the expected value of OBJ,
require; obligate; force; command; inverse of "allow"; opposite of "forbid"; SBJ requires OBJ (obligation; requirement) to happen,
allow; permit; may; inverse of "require"; negation of "forbid"; SBJ allows OBJ (privilage; permission) to happen,
want; desire; SBJ wants OBJ to happen,
intend; will; SBJ intends to make OBJ happen,
be willing; SBJ is willing to make OBJ happen,
try; attempt; intend; SBJ tries to make OBJ happen,
have; possess; own; SBJ (owner) possesses OBJ (property),
go; come; move; travel; from to; SBJ goes from IND to OBJ,
perceive; look; listen; sniff; taste; SBJ actively perceives OBJ (signal; sight; sound; scent); contrast with "be perceptible",
be perceptible; be visible; see; be audible; hear; be smellable; smell; be tasteable; taste; be feelable; feel; OBJ passively perceives SBJ (sensation); contrast with "perceive",
emit; say; loud; bright; strong; SBJ releases OBJ (message; utterance) to IND (recipient; listener; viewer) (AMOUNT:volume; amplitude; brightness); antonym of "quiet",
be quiet; dim; soft; faint; weak SBJ is quiet; antonym of "emit",cuc, ono ʃ
communicate; take; correspond; SBJ has a two-way interaction with OBJ (interlocutor) about IND (topic; conversation; passage) (TOOL:language),
give; converse of "receive"; SBJ (giver) gives OBJ (gift) to IND (recipient),
take; SBJ (taker) takes OBJ (gain) from IND (loser),
be tangible; be physical; SBJ (object) is tangible; antonym of "intangible",
be intangible; be nonphysical; SBJ (concept) is intangible; antonym of "tangible",
hold; carry; have on one's person; SBJ carries OBJ,
be many; SBJ (set; group) contains many elements (AMOUNT:number; count; whole number),
go through; SBJ does an action into and then out of OBJ (tube; hallway)
be between; SBJ exists in line with and between OBJ and IND,
be probable; be sure; Bayesian probability; SBJ is likely to happen according to OBJ (AMOUNT:probability); antonym of "skeptical",
be improbable; be skeptical; Bayesian improbability; SBJ is unlikely to happen according to OBJ; antonym of "sure",
seem; believe; OBJ (believer) accepts that SBJ (apparent; seeming) is true on a subconcious level; contrast with "appear",
appear; think; OBJ (thinker; accepter) conciously decides that SBJ is true; contrast with "seem",
be good; be pleasing; like; OBJ likes SBJ (preference; favourite) (AMOUNT:goodness; preference level); antonym of "bad",
be bad; be unpleasant; dislike; OBJ dislikes SBJ (anathema; least favourite); antonym of "good",
be more; be greater; be much; SBJ (a lot; more) is numerically greater than OBJ; antonym of "less",
be same; be none; SBJ has the same numerical value as OBJ,
be less; be little; SBJ (a bit; less) is numerically less than OBJ; antonym of "more",
be old; length of time; applies to objects an events as well as people; SBJ (senior citizen) is old (AMOUNT:age); antonym of "young",
be young; length of time; applies to objects and events as well as people; SBJ (kid) is young; antonym of "old",
be late; after; positive time; SBJ (future (DATIVE:past tense)) happens after OBJ (AMOUNT:time); antonym of "early",
be early; before; negative time; SBJ (past (DATIVE:past tense)) happens before OBJ; antonym of "late",
be big; large; SBJ has a high volume (AMOUNT:size; volume); antonym of "small",
be small; little; SBJ has a low volume; antonym of "big",
be long; tall; maximum physical dimension; SBJ (stick; rod; strand) is long (AMOUNT:length); see "old"; antonym of "short",
be short; maximum physical dimension; SBJ (nub) is short; see "young"; antonym of "long",
be broad; middle dimension; SBJ is broad (AMOUNT:breadth); antonym of "narrow",
be narrow; middle dimension; SBJ is narrow; antonym of "broad",
be thick; minimum dimension; SBJ (slab) is thick (AMOUNT:thickness); antonym of "thin",
be thin; minimum dimension; SBJ (sheet) is thin; antonym of "thick",
be far; distant; SBJ is physically or numerically far from OBJ (AMOUNT:distance); antonym of "near",
be near; close; SBJ is physically or numerically close to OBJ; antonym of "far",

be down; SBJ (bottom; downside) has a higher _z_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view (AMOUNT:_z_ coordinate); antonym of "up"; usually synonomous with "low" in which case "down" is preferred,
be up; SBJ (top; upside) has a lower _z_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view; antonym of "down"; usually synonomous with "high" in which case "up" is preferred,
be forward; frontward; SBJ (front; field of view) has a higher _y_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view (AMOUNT:_y_ coordinate); antonym of "backward",
be backward; SBJ (back; behind) has a lower _y_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view; antonym of "forward",
be right; SBJ (right side) has a higher _x_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view (AMOUNT:_z_ coordinate); antonym of "left",
be left; SBJ (left side) has a lower _x_ coordinate than OBJ from IND's point of view; antonym of "right",
be wide; obtuse; big; large; SBJ (splotch; blotch) spans a wide angle from the point of view of OBJ (AMOUNT:angle;angular size); antonym of "narrow",
be narrow; acute; small; little; SBJ (dot; point) spans a narrow angle from the point of view of OBJ (LOCATION:edge; blade); antonym of "wide",
be below; up; SBJ (header; top) appears below OBJ from the point of view of IND (AMOUNT:altitude; distance down page); antonym of "above",
be above; down; SBJ (footer; bottom) appears below OBJ from the point of view of IND; antonym of "below",
be starboard; right; SBJ appears to the right of OBJ from the point of view of IND (AMOUNT:bearing; azimuth angle; distance across page); antonym of "port",
be port; left; SBJ appears to the left of OBJ from the point of view of IND; antonym of "starboard",

be widdershins; counterclockwise; SBJ appears rotated widdershins from the orientation OBJ (original orientation; right-side up) from the point of view of IND (AMOUNT:orientation; rotation); antonym of "clockwise",
be clockwise; SBJ appears rotated clockwise from the orientation OBJ from the point of view of IND; antonym of "widdershins",

be low; SBJ (ground; earth; depths) has a lower altitude than OBJ (standard altitude; usually sea level) based on the planet IND (AMOUNT:elevation; altitude); antonym of "high"; usually synonomous with "down" in which case "down" is preferred,
be high; SBJ (sky; cosmos) has a higher altitude than OBJ based on the planet IND; antonym of "low"; usually synonomous with "up" in which case "up" is preferred,
be south; SBJ has a lower latitude than OBJ (standard parallel; usually the North Pole) based on the planet IND (AMOUNT:latitude); antonym of "north",
be north; SBJ has a higher latitude than OBJ based on the planet IND; antonym of "south",
be east; SBJ has a higher longitude than OBJ (standard meridian; prime meridian) based on the planet IND (AMOUNT:longitude); antonym of "west",
be west; SBJ has a lower longitude than OBJ based on the planet IND; antonym of "east",
be moral; good; if SBJ (good deed; moral) happens, it will be morally good (AMOUNT:morality; goodness); antonym of "evil",
be evil; immoral; bad; if SBJ (evil; sin) happens, it will be morally bad; antonym of "moral",
be skillful; effective; good; SBJ is good at causing OBJ (AMOUNT:skill level); antonym of "inept",
be inept; unskillful; ineffective; bad; SBJ is bad at causing OBJ; antonym of "skillful",
be apt; SBJ fits the situation OBJ well (AMOUNT:aptitude); antonym of "inapt",
be inapt; SBJ fail to fit the situation OBJ well; antonym of "apt",
work; productive; SBJ (worker) works to make OBJ (job; work) happen,
index; SBJ has a position in OBJ (list; order) (AMOUNT:position; index),
be next; SBJ (next) is next, after OBJ (previous) in the set IND (sequence),
track; SBJ (tracker; follower) follows OBJ (path; course),
lead; command; SBJ (leader) leads the actions of OBJ (follower),
be found; OBJ knows where SBJ is,
notice; OBJ is conciously aware of the presence of SBJ,
denote; mean; SBJ (signal; word) means OBJ (definition; meaning),
call; SBJ (caller) calls OBJ (callee) remotely and digitally,
relate; SBJ is genetically related to OBJ (relative; kin; blood),
accompany; come with; SBJ (companion; partner; company) accompanies OBJ,
show; SBJ (shower) encourages and enables IND (audience) to passively perceive OBJ (show),
jostle; move; SBJ deforms and moves in place,
among; among the object, which is a set,
write; record; save a file; SBJ (writer) writes OBJ (writing; data) on IND (record) (TOOL:writing utensil|LOCATION:desk; writing surface),
read; derive meaning from a physical object; load a file; SBJ (reader) reads OBJ (reading; data) from IND (source),
wall off; SBJ (wall; roadblock) walls off IND (outdoors; outside; other side) from OBJ (room; indoors; inside; this side),
be outer; be outside; SBJ is many layers away from the center of OBJ (structure); antonym of "inner",
be inner; be inside; SBJ is many layers near the center of OBJ; antonym of "outer",
timeliness; for meetings and such, or habitually,
tardiness; for meetings and such, or habitually,
eat; drink; SBJ (eater) eats OBJ (food),njam,ono njam njam
set; be in a discrete collection with a finite number of other entities,
categorize; place something in a category; interpret something as belonging in a group,
systemize; place something in a system; interpret something as being part of a whole,
primary; refers to generally being main or central,
fringe; refers to being secondary or minor,
traverse; typically compounded to make things like "swim", "climb", "gallop", etc.,
hand-off; exchange direct object via hands,
fast; magnitude of time derivative of position,
slow; unmagnitude of time derivative of position,
love romantically; infatuation; SBJ (lover) is in love with OBJ (love),
love platonically; SBJ loves OBJ (family member; close friend) platonically,
problem; to pose a challenge, but not necessarily in a bad way,
buy; purchase; SBJ (buyer; customer) legally obtains OBJ (good; service) from IND (vendor) (TOOL:money; currency),
wide; angular distance with indirect object being centrum,
acute; angular closeness with indirect object being centrum,
business-open; can refer to activity in general,
business-closed; can refer to dormancy in general,
craze; act erratically or illogically; does not necessarily refer to mental illness,
level; general discrete measure of progress,
lag; general discrete measure of backwardness,
sentience; I'm not going to try to define it here; I have a definition, but it cannot be put into words,
apply; the subject is a process, the direct object is something that undergoes that process,
private; be concealed or sheltered from the world,
sector-public; be in the public sector,
sector-private; be in the private sector,
frequent; rate at which something oscillates, progresses, or decays with respect to time,
periodic; inverse of rate at which something oscillates, progresses, or decays with respect to time,
be dense; be frequent; be common; be tightly packed; SBJ occurs frequently and close together in OBJ (space; interval; bounds); antonym of "sparse",
be sparse; be infrequent; be uncommon; be loosely distributed; SBJ is few and far between in OBJ; antonym of "dense",
be heavy; SBJ is heavy (AMOUNT:weight); antonym of "lightweight",
pulse; oscillate; flash; beat,tumtum,ono dudum dudum
easy; of the subject for the direct object,
difficult; of the subject for the direct object,
convert; as in a rate or ratio,
care; believe that something merits concern on a subconcious level; contrast with "deem-important",
deem-important; think that something is worthy of concern and act as such; contrast with "care",
rest; be on; SBJ rests on OBJ,
grip; SBJ exerts a frictional force on OBJ,
recept; receive something sent, not something given,
bureaucrate; be a bureaucrat in a bureaucracy,
recall; draw a fact from memory; contrast with related concepts "can-remember" and "memorize",
broken; having fallen apart or cracked,
cyan; stimulation of M and S cones,
magenta; stimulation of L and S cones,
yellow; stimulation of L and M cones,
hue; expressed colloquially as a color name, not an angle,
color; ojbect is a color value, not a number,
jump; over the indirect object onto the direct object,
play; a game or a sport,
rescind; progress to a goal or agenda,
staff; provide support in a manner not directly related to the main thing,
available; time management at a point,
join; be in a group of people; SBJ (member) is a part of OBJ (group; party; club; organization),
action-take; the direct object is the action,
step; the direct object is what you step on or in,
late; +t; like "after", but more numeric and detail-oriented,
model; replicate; image; SBJ (modeler) makes OBJ (image; model) after IND (source; original),
patronize; as in a customer going to a business,
lead-to; be a door; subject is door, direct object is thing on other side, indirect object is thing on this side,
think-of; come up with an idea,
prosper; well; good; SBJ does well,
grateful; thankful; OBJ feels grateful to SBJ,
sorry; apologetic; SBJ feels sorry for causing OBJ to happen,
sympathise; SBJ sympathises with OBJ for IND happening,
swallow; suck; consume whole,kulup,ono glup glup glup
have sex; fuck; bang; nail; do; plow; ride,
anticipating; like "forward-to-look", but not necessarily positive,
hungry; for food, sex, sleep, etc.,
pleased; basic euphoria from food, music, or sex,
proud; the happiness associated with feeling like a productive member of society,
satisfied; the good feeling produced by snapping parts together or popping bubble wrap,
terrified; the brief reaction to jump-scares that comes before actual fear or annoyance,
troubled; have troubled feelings from the direct object,
puzzled; have confusion from the direct object,
also-happen; describes things that happen in tandem,
beside; to be on the side of,
in-season; a time of year when something is "in",
sharp; of an edge or blade,
dull; of an edge or blade,
into; direct object is long/deep thing,
out-of; direct object is long/deep thing,
embark; in the metaphorical sense; begin a long habitual process,
finish; end a long habitual process,
structural-strong; resistance to breaking bending or deforming,
brittle; tendency to shatter when force is applied, without bending,
flexible; tendency to bend when force is applied,
test; science; investigate; observe; experiment; SBJ (scientist) carefully conducts experiments and observations to learn the answer to or more about OBJ (hypothesis; field of study; big question),
engineer; SBJ (engineer) uses technical skills and fine problem-solving to solve OBJ (technical problem),
entrepreneur; SBJ (entrepreneur) uses ideation, people skills, and determination to solve OBJ (largescale problem),
hit; intentionally cause a collision with something,
flash; quickly emit bright light; also applies to sound and other sensations,
cook; boil; steam; broil; marinate; grill; smoke; bake; toast; microwave,
oppressed; depend; control; powerful; OBJ (oppressor) controls SBJ (oppressed),
appealing; of a picture, sound, etc.,
unappealing; of a picture, sound, etc.,
oppose; compete; fight; SBJ (opposer) works toward a goal contrary to that of OBJ (opponent; competitor),
fight; SBJ (fighter) has an adversarial engagement with OBJ (adversary; opponent),
entertain; as in a movie, play, or skit,
downstream; combine it with "become" to get "flow",
act; behave as though the direct object is true; do things in a certain manner,
wave; a hand or a flag,
lame; the slangy definition, not the disability one,
live; as in live a life,
expert; a person who is not a layperson,
physical; describes things in the physical realm,
name; indirect object is person, direct object is name,
print; convert a digital object into a real one,
drunk; applies to alcohol as well as other drugs,
function; do what one is supposed to,
rapid; of communication; the idea with this word is to distinguish rapid SMS texting from lethargic email,
laggy; of communication; the idea with this word is to distinguish lethargic email from rapid SMS texting,
bladder-full; the feeling of having to pee,
screen; project or render images onto a surface,
elastic; tendency to bend and then spring back,
classy; the quality of being expensive and unneccesary,
attention; be occupied by the direct object; see "emit",
tangle; knot; SBJ (knot) is tangled together,

touch; meet; join; SBJ and OBJ are so close to each other that they cannot physically get any closer (please don't get tecnical with my definition of this) (LOCATION:joint; corner; intersection; edge),
hunt; chase; pursue; SBJ (hunter) hunts for OBJ (hunted), either literally or metaphorically,
deserve; be entitled; SBJ (worthy; deserving; entitled) deserves OBJ (dessert)
